        <p>Transform your digital presence in {{ pageData.city }} with advanced {{ pageData.service }} strategies that prioritize actual revenue over vanity metrics.</p>
        <p>I dive deep into data, track every conversion, and aggressively optimize to ensure you get the absolute best return on investment in your market.</p>
      {% endif %}
      
      <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin-top: 24px; color:var(--text-muted); display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;">
        {% if pageData.service == "WordPress Website Development" or pageData.service == "SEO" %}
