        <li><strong style="color:var(--text);">✔ Technical Excellence:</strong> Clean code and robust architecture.</li>
        <li><strong style="color:var(--text);">✔ Long-Term ROI:</strong> Assets that generate value for years.</li>
        {% elif pageData.service == "Graphic Design" or pageData.service == "Video Editing" or pageData.service == "Social Media Management" %}
